import PyPDF2
with open('./14-EmojiCrypt/EmojiCrypt-main/paper.pdf', 'rb') as f:
    reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(f)
    text = ''
    for page in reader.pages[:5]:
        text += page.extract_text() + '\n'
print(text[:2000])
